</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_desktop_services__get_desktop_changed_handling" kindref="compound">GetDesktopChangedHandling</ref>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Gets the reference counted interface that allows registering and unregistering for notifications when desktop settings change.    </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_desktop_services__get_desktops" kindref="compound">GetDesktops</ref>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Gets the reference counted list of desktops instantiated on the AMD GPUs.    </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_desktop_services__get_number_of_desktops" kindref="compound">GetNumberOfDesktops</ref>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Gets the number of desktops instantiated on the AMD GPUs.    </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_desktop_services__get_simple_eyefinity" kindref="compound">GetSimpleEyefinity</ref>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Gets the reference counted interface to create and destroy AMD Eyefinity desktops.   </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
